primary.context: Caller is experiencing login issues with an invalid account number error and previously sent links failed.
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller and sent a payment link via email and text after the caller declined a portal registration link.

steps: Caller identified herself and reported an invalid account number issue.
Agent performed account lookup via phone number and verified identity (name and state).
Agent offered a Clubhouse registration link, which the caller rejected because a previous one failed.
Agent clarified the intent was to make a payment.
Agent confirmed property and contract details.
Agent confirmed contact information and sent the payment link.

clarifications.note: Agent asked to confirm name spelling for verification.

insights.summary: The caller wanted to make a payment after encountering errors with her account number and a previous registration link. The agent successfully verified her and sent a new payment link via text and email.
insights.verbatim: I'm trying to get into my account. The account number is wrong... You sent me [a link] already and it did not work.
